# --- Build artifacts (all apps) — safety net, never commit these ---
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/dist/
**/.turbo/
**/__pycache__/
**/.DS_Store

# --- Secrets (all apps) — never commit; keep keys local per machine ---
**/.secret_key
**/.env.local
**/.env
